WEBVTT

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:03.190
Hey, good morning family. Well, I have a

00:00:03.200 --> 00:00:05.030
hard word to give, but first

00:00:05.040 --> 00:00:06.789
off, I want to tell you all thank you

00:00:06.799 --> 00:00:08.790
for praying for me. Thank you for being

00:00:08.800 --> 00:00:10.950
here and being a part of this

00:00:10.960 --> 00:00:12.549
family, this prayer channel. You know, I

00:00:12.559 --> 00:00:14.870
was going to do this word yesterday and

00:00:14.880 --> 00:00:16.550
I was going to tell you what the Lord is

00:00:16.560 --> 00:00:18.870
showing me concerning America and what's

00:00:18.880 --> 00:00:20.950
coming. But I didn't want to come out

00:00:20.960 --> 00:00:22.390
and just give it. I wanted to pray over

00:00:22.400 --> 00:00:24.470
it. Yesterday, like I said, I

00:00:24.480 --> 00:00:25.750
was driving around and the Lord gave me

00:00:25.760 --> 00:00:27.269
the word. He said, 'I want you to go

00:00:27.279 --> 00:00:29.109
home and I want you to dig in the

00:00:29.109 --> 00:00:29.119
flower

00:00:29.119 --> 00:00:31.029
beds. I want you to go outside and

00:00:31.039 --> 00:00:33.110
pull weeds right now.'I said, 'Well,

00:00:33.120 --> 00:00:34.790
I'm going to go in and do the

00:00:34.790 --> 00:00:34.800
video.'He

00:00:34.800 --> 00:00:35.830
said, 'No, you're not. You're going to

00:00:35.840 --> 00:00:38.389
go outside and pull

00:00:38.389 --> 00:00:38.399
weeds.'I

00:00:38.399 --> 00:00:41.430
said, 'Yes, sir.'So, I was

00:00:41.440 --> 00:00:43.030
out there just praying in the spirit and

00:00:43.040 --> 00:00:45.350
just pulling weeds in the flower bed all

00:00:45.360 --> 00:00:48.470
afternoon

00:00:48.480 --> 00:00:49.910
and just praying and asking Him, 'So,

00:00:49.920 --> 00:00:51.430
what do you want me to say?'And He

00:00:51.430 --> 00:00:51.440
said,

00:00:51.440 --> 00:00:54.950
'Nothing yet. Go low. Go slow. Go low

00:00:54.960 --> 00:00:57.110
inside. Go deep inside. Pray in the

00:00:57.120 --> 00:00:59.670
spirit and go slow about it. Don't

00:00:59.680 --> 00:01:01.430
be quick to deliver a word. There's no

00:01:01.430 --> 00:01:01.440
urgency.'And

00:01:01.440 --> 00:01:03.430
He gave me the scriptures.

00:01:03.440 --> 00:01:05.990
He said, 'Ephesians

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:09.350
5:1: Be an imitator of God, as dear

00:01:09.360 --> 00:01:12.550
children imitate

00:01:12.560 --> 00:01:15.510
their earthly fathers. Imitate the

00:01:15.510 --> 00:01:15.520
Lord.'And

00:01:15.520 --> 00:01:17.510
I was like, 'So what do you mean by

00:01:17.510 --> 00:01:17.520
that?'And

00:01:17.520 --> 00:01:19.990
He started talking about how

00:01:20.000 --> 00:01:23.109
He wasn't quick to go out and

00:01:23.119 --> 00:01:25.910
raise Lazarus from the dead. The urgency

00:01:25.920 --> 00:01:27.670
was there and everybody was pushing Him,

00:01:27.680 --> 00:01:29.990
saying, 'Lazarus is sick. He's

00:01:29.990 --> 00:01:30.000
dying,'and

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:32.950
all the things were going

00:01:32.950 --> 00:01:32.960
around—all

00:01:32.960 --> 00:01:35.830
the voices around Him. He

00:01:35.840 --> 00:01:39.590
was hearing Lazarus is sick and dying,

00:01:39.600 --> 00:01:41.429
and all the voices around Him were

00:01:41.439 --> 00:01:43.190
trying to pressure Him to move out of

00:01:43.200 --> 00:01:45.190
what God was telling Him to do, which was stay

00:01:45.200 --> 00:01:48.310
still, peace,

00:01:48.320 --> 00:01:51.350
peace. Four days go by, and Jesus goes,

00:01:51.360 --> 00:01:54.870
and they said, 'He stinks,

00:01:54.870 --> 00:01:54.880
Lord.'So

00:01:54.880 --> 00:01:56.950
there was no urgency in His

00:01:56.960 --> 00:01:58.630
spirit except to follow what the Father had

00:01:58.640 --> 00:02:01.350
told Him to do. Then He started bringing

00:02:01.360 --> 00:02:05.270
up Mary and Martha. Mary was

00:02:05.280 --> 00:02:08.150
sitting at the feet of Jesus,

00:02:08.160 --> 00:02:11.110
listening to Him, staying vertical. She

00:02:11.120 --> 00:02:13.030
didn't do what Martha was doing. Martha

00:02:13.040 --> 00:02:14.710
was in there probably throwing pots

00:02:14.720 --> 00:02:17.110
and pans around, getting all upset

00:02:17.120 --> 00:02:18.710
because nobody was in

00:02:18.720 --> 00:02:20.070
there helping her, because she felt it

00:02:20.080 --> 00:02:22.790
was urgent to cook

00:02:22.800 --> 00:02:24.790
the food for all the disciples and

00:02:24.800 --> 00:02:27.190
for Jesus. And so Mary

00:02:27.190 --> 00:02:27.200
is

00:02:27.200 --> 00:02:29.750
doing what we should be doing, staying

00:02:29.760 --> 00:02:32.630
at the feet of Jesus. There's no urgency

00:02:32.640 --> 00:02:34.550
when you're in

00:02:34.560 --> 00:02:36.869
peace like that, is what the Lord was

00:02:36.879 --> 00:02:39.750
showing me. Be an imitator of God. What

00:02:39.760 --> 00:02:42.869
did Jesus do? He stayed, and He heard the

00:02:42.879 --> 00:02:45.750
Father's voice concerning Lazarus.

00:02:45.760 --> 00:02:48.150
And what did Mary do? She stayed

00:02:48.160 --> 00:02:49.750
at His feet. Martha was out there doing

00:02:49.760 --> 00:02:51.830
all the busy work,

00:02:51.840 --> 00:02:53.190
but she should have been at the feet,

00:02:53.200 --> 00:02:55.670
too. The urgency of the hour is staying

00:02:55.680 --> 00:02:58.309
at the feet of Jesus, not being moved by

00:02:58.319 --> 00:02:59.910
the circumstances of what you're seeing

00:02:59.920 --> 00:03:01.830
in the news, thinking, 'I've got to come out and tell

00:03:01.840 --> 00:03:03.270
everybody what the Lord

00:03:03.270 --> 00:03:03.280
is saying.'And

00:03:03.280 --> 00:03:07.110
the Lord said, 'No, pull

00:03:07.110 --> 00:03:07.120
weeds.'I

00:03:07.120 --> 00:03:09.030
said, 'Whoa, I don't

00:03:09.030 --> 00:03:09.040
understand.'But

00:03:09.040 --> 00:03:10.550
it's called dying to self, and

00:03:10.560 --> 00:03:12.149
it's His channel. And that's what He was

00:03:12.159 --> 00:03:14.070
trying to get across to me: no matter

00:03:14.080 --> 00:03:15.670
how much you think you need to

00:03:15.680 --> 00:03:17.430
deliver a word because you know it's

00:03:17.440 --> 00:03:21.430
important, this is more important.

00:03:21.440 --> 00:03:23.750
'I need you to rest.

00:03:23.760 --> 00:03:26.229
I need you to stay right here at my feet

00:03:26.239 --> 00:03:28.309
right now, vertical. There's much

00:03:28.319 --> 00:03:30.550
that I need to talk to you about. And

00:03:30.560 --> 00:03:32.949
the only way you're going to hear what

00:03:32.959 --> 00:03:34.949
I'm going to tell you is by staying

00:03:34.959 --> 00:03:38.470
right here like Mary.

00:03:40.640 --> 00:03:43.270
Don't be Martha right now, Brandon. Stay

00:03:43.280 --> 00:03:45.110
at my feet.'There are a lot of people

00:03:45.120 --> 00:03:47.110
being Marthas, and they're running

00:03:47.120 --> 00:03:48.869
around trying to make the first video

00:03:48.879 --> 00:03:50.949
and be the first. He said, 'But it's

00:03:50.959 --> 00:03:52.710
more important to be accurate, and the

00:03:52.720 --> 00:03:54.710
only way you stay accurate is staying at

00:03:54.720 --> 00:03:57.350
my feet. Pull

00:03:57.350 --> 00:03:57.360
weeds.'And

00:03:57.360 --> 00:03:59.270
I was like, you know, you have

00:03:59.280 --> 00:04:00.869
all these things going, 'Well, I've got

00:04:00.869 --> 00:04:00.879
to

00:04:00.879 --> 00:04:07.110
pull weeds. Be

00:04:07.110 --> 00:04:07.120
still.'Do

00:04:07.120 --> 00:04:08.550
you know how hard it

00:04:08.550 --> 00:04:08.560
is

00:04:08.560 --> 00:04:09.750
sometimes when you feel like you

00:04:09.760 --> 00:04:10.949
haven't heard the word and you're going,

00:04:10.959 --> 00:04:12.789
'Well, Lord, you gave me the word,

00:04:12.789 --> 00:04:12.799
so...'But

00:04:12.799 --> 00:04:14.470
here I

00:04:14.480 --> 00:04:16.469
was, and I started praying in the spirit,

00:04:16.479 --> 00:04:18.150
and you know what He started doing? He

00:04:18.160 --> 00:04:21.509
started showing me flowers.

00:04:21.519 --> 00:04:23.189
I started praying

00:04:23.189 --> 00:04:23.199
in

00:04:23.199 --> 00:04:24.310
the spirit and I'm looking and

00:04:24.320 --> 00:04:25.510
seeing if He's going to show me anything

00:04:25.520 --> 00:04:26.950
else, and He started showing me

00:04:26.960 --> 00:04:29.670
flowers. I saw beautiful lavender

00:04:29.680 --> 00:04:32.710
flowers that looked like heaven. It was

00:04:32.720 --> 00:04:35.909
glimpses, and I started weeping because

00:04:35.909 --> 00:04:35.919
of

00:04:35.919 --> 00:04:37.590
the beauty of the flowers. And He

00:04:37.600 --> 00:04:38.950
said, 'Remember, just like George

00:04:38.960 --> 00:04:41.430
Washington Carver, Brandon. He was the man

00:04:41.440 --> 00:04:43.189
that talked with the flowers, and

00:04:43.199 --> 00:04:45.590
God showed him the secret things because

00:04:45.600 --> 00:04:48.870
he put God first, and he didn't let

00:04:48.880 --> 00:04:52.550
the clutter cloud his

00:04:52.560 --> 00:04:55.430
mind of what was going on around him. He

00:04:55.440 --> 00:04:57.110
took time to spend with the Great

00:04:57.120 --> 00:04:58.870
Creator every single day at four o'clock

00:04:58.880 --> 00:05:01.030
in the morning. And no matter how much

00:05:01.040 --> 00:05:03.030
was going around him, he would always

00:05:03.040 --> 00:05:05.670
talk to the peanut, and the peanut

00:05:05.680 --> 00:05:07.510
shared its secrets with

00:05:07.510 --> 00:05:07.520
him.'George

00:05:07.520 --> 00:05:09.189
Washington Carver was a great man of

00:05:09.199 --> 00:05:13.029
God. And so I want to tell you, for what

00:05:13.039 --> 00:05:16.870
I'm about to tell you, this came

00:05:16.870 --> 00:05:16.880
later—more

00:05:16.880 --> 00:05:19.110
of what He was showing me is in

00:05:19.120 --> 00:05:22.070
store: 'A great shaking to

00:05:22.070 --> 00:05:22.080
awaken.'He

00:05:22.080 --> 00:05:24.710
keeps talking to me about it. And

00:05:24.710 --> 00:05:24.720
at

00:05:24.720 --> 00:05:28.550
this time, I was so tired.

00:05:28.560 --> 00:05:30.950
I was dozing off, and all of a

00:05:30.960 --> 00:05:32.950
sudden He wanted to talk more about

00:05:32.960 --> 00:05:35.510
what's coming, and I

00:05:35.510 --> 00:05:35.520
had

00:05:35.520 --> 00:05:37.590
heavy eyes. I was on the

00:05:37.600 --> 00:05:39.590
couch, and I was bobbing, doing

00:05:39.600 --> 00:05:41.749
the old bob. All of a sudden,

00:05:41.759 --> 00:05:43.510
He said, 'I have something to

00:05:43.510 --> 00:05:43.520
say.'And

00:05:43.520 --> 00:05:45.590
I went, 'Yes, sir. What's going

00:05:45.590 --> 00:05:45.600
on?'You

00:05:45.600 --> 00:05:48.230
know, and I started praying, and I'm

00:05:48.240 --> 00:05:50.629
talking down low. I said,

00:05:50.639 --> 00:05:52.150
'Well, Lord, you picked a real fine

00:05:52.150 --> 00:05:52.160
time.'But

00:05:52.160 --> 00:05:53.670
it's not in my time; it's in

00:05:53.680 --> 00:05:55.590
Yours. It was when my flesh was out

00:05:55.600 --> 00:05:58.550
of the way. I was completely exhausted,

00:05:58.560 --> 00:06:00.710
and I told my son, 'Grab the

00:06:00.710 --> 00:06:00.720
recorder.'I

00:06:00.720 --> 00:06:02.550
said, 'The Father's

00:06:02.560 --> 00:06:04.390
going to talk, and I'm really

00:06:04.400 --> 00:06:05.670
tired right now, but I'm going to say

00:06:05.680 --> 00:06:07.830
what He says.'But I was dead to my flesh at

00:06:07.840 --> 00:06:09.749
that point instead of being like a

00:06:09.759 --> 00:06:11.749
chicken with its head cut off, flapping

00:06:11.749 --> 00:06:11.759
its

00:06:11.759 --> 00:06:14.710
wings all around. It was

00:06:14.720 --> 00:06:16.230
at the time when my flesh was out of

00:06:16.240 --> 00:06:18.629
the way and He could talk the loudest.

00:06:18.639 --> 00:06:20.870
And I said, 'You know, Lord, You really

00:06:20.880 --> 00:06:23.990
are so amazing to me.''Focus on the

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:26.870
flowers today, Brandon.

00:06:26.880 --> 00:06:28.469
Focus on the flowers.'And there will be

00:06:28.479 --> 00:06:30.230
a lot of you who say, 'Oh, Brandon, get

00:06:30.240 --> 00:06:33.430
to it.'I just did.

00:06:33.440 --> 00:06:35.830
I just did. I just told you a vital

00:06:35.840 --> 00:06:39.029
piece of the puzzle that many of you

00:06:39.039 --> 00:06:41.189
will try to bypass because you're so

00:06:41.199 --> 00:06:43.670
busy. But like the Lord is always

00:06:43.680 --> 00:06:45.029
telling me, He said, 'You're in a hurry

00:06:45.039 --> 00:06:46.950
to go nowhere.

00:06:46.960 --> 00:06:48.629
Nothing else matters. Everything that

00:06:48.639 --> 00:06:50.230
you're trying to achieve on this earth

00:06:50.240 --> 00:06:52.950
is going to be gone.'Most people are

00:06:52.960 --> 00:06:55.909
trying to build their

00:06:55.919 --> 00:06:58.070
future and all these great things, the

00:06:58.080 --> 00:07:00.390
wealth and all the things on this earth.

00:07:00.400 --> 00:07:02.710
But the Lord said to me, 'Brandon,

00:07:02.710 --> 00:07:02.720
sow

00:07:02.720 --> 00:07:05.350
the seeds for the thousand years.

00:07:05.350 --> 00:07:05.360
Sow

00:07:05.360 --> 00:07:07.270
the seeds for what you'll reap

00:07:07.280 --> 00:07:08.870
on the other side. For what you sow in

00:07:08.880 --> 00:07:11.029
secret, you'll be rewarded

00:07:11.029 --> 00:07:11.039
openly.'So,

00:07:11.039 --> 00:07:13.189
this is what I saw. You know, a lot of

00:07:13.199 --> 00:07:15.189
people are focused on the peace

00:07:15.199 --> 00:07:16.309
agreement. They're saying,

00:07:16.319 --> 00:07:18.790
'Hey, we're going to have a

00:07:18.800 --> 00:07:20.710
ceasefire and all these

00:07:20.710 --> 00:07:20.720
things.'And

00:07:20.720 --> 00:07:22.870
if you go back to the video

00:07:22.870 --> 00:07:22.880
where

00:07:22.880 --> 00:07:24.870
I was praying—I gave a short on

00:07:24.880 --> 00:07:27.430
it back in December—the Lord showed

00:07:27.440 --> 00:07:28.870
me that they'll call peace and safety.

00:07:28.880 --> 00:07:31.110
There'll be peace agreements. So, we

00:07:31.120 --> 00:07:33.189
go to what the Lord's already

00:07:33.199 --> 00:07:35.430
showed us, and now we're seeing it in

00:07:35.440 --> 00:07:38.070
the news seven months later. Seven

00:07:38.080 --> 00:07:40.150
months later,

00:07:40.160 --> 00:07:42.390
and He's warning about sudden

00:07:42.400 --> 00:07:46.469
destruction, major attacks still coming.

00:07:46.479 --> 00:07:49.830
They are not satisfied with what they

00:07:49.840 --> 00:07:54.150
have achieved. Iran is saying

00:07:54.150 --> 00:07:54.160
this

00:07:54.160 --> 00:07:55.830
because they lost so much. They

00:07:55.840 --> 00:07:58.629
dumped billions and billions of dollars

00:07:58.639 --> 00:08:01.430
into their nuclear program

00:08:01.440 --> 00:08:03.909
and it was completely wiped out. A lot

00:08:03.919 --> 00:08:05.990
of it—I don't think all of it, in

00:08:06.000 --> 00:08:08.230
my opinion, of what I've seen in the

00:08:08.240 --> 00:08:11.749
spirit. Not all of it, but a big majority of

00:08:11.759 --> 00:08:14.390
it. And the Lord showed me still to come

00:08:14.400 --> 00:08:19.270
a major revival in Iran—a major, major

00:08:19.280 --> 00:08:22.150
revival. As they're distracted, the

00:08:22.160 --> 00:08:24.629
infrastructure of things is going to be

00:08:24.639 --> 00:08:28.950
very crippled, set back by decades.

00:08:28.960 --> 00:08:30.869
The Lord said, 'like the Stone Age,

00:08:30.879 --> 00:08:32.709
back in the decades,'because they're

00:08:32.719 --> 00:08:35.509
going to be delayed big time. But I saw

00:08:35.519 --> 00:08:36.949
infrastructure problems with the

00:08:36.959 --> 00:08:40.070
electricity, with a lot of things.

00:08:40.080 --> 00:08:43.990
And the Lord even talked about oil. So

00:08:44.000 --> 00:08:45.829
with all that being said, what was the

00:08:45.839 --> 00:08:48.070
next thing I told you? I warned you

00:08:48.080 --> 00:08:51.990
about a biological attack coming out

00:08:52.000 --> 00:08:54.710
of Syria. And many people, when they saw

00:08:54.720 --> 00:08:56.949
the World War II video, they said,

00:08:56.959 --> 00:08:58.630
'Brandon, you said there would be a

00:08:58.640 --> 00:09:02.070
great betrayal.'And I said,

00:09:04.080 --> 00:09:07.509
'Wait, it's still coming. Wait, it's

00:09:07.519 --> 00:09:10.470
still coming.'I see these are

00:09:10.480 --> 00:09:11.990
different visions for different

00:09:12.000 --> 00:09:14.150
scenarios, and it's not all about what's

00:09:14.160 --> 00:09:16.070
happening right now. This is like an

00:09:16.080 --> 00:09:19.190
onion; it has a lot of layers.

00:09:19.200 --> 00:09:21.269
And the next thing I believe we're going

00:09:21.279 --> 00:09:25.910
to see is a major attack against Syria

00:09:25.920 --> 00:09:29.430
as Iran retaliates. And the

00:09:29.430 --> 00:09:29.440
Houthis,

00:09:29.440 --> 00:09:31.990
the rebels, and these people out of Syria

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:35.829
will use some kind of biological weapon,

00:09:35.839 --> 00:09:38.310
and they will attack them, and Damascus

00:09:38.320 --> 00:09:41.829
will become a ruinous heap

00:09:41.839 --> 00:09:45.269
when this takes place. I saw Turkey

00:09:45.279 --> 00:09:47.910
come to the aid of a wounded brother. I

00:09:47.920 --> 00:09:49.829
even have the video. This is exactly

00:09:49.839 --> 00:09:52.070
what the Lord said: they will

00:09:52.080 --> 00:09:54.310
come to the aid of a wounded brother, and

00:09:54.320 --> 00:09:56.949
all the other Arab nations will be

00:09:56.959 --> 00:10:00.070
furious when Israel strikes Syria in the

00:10:00.080 --> 00:10:01.910
days ahead.

00:10:01.920 --> 00:10:04.630
They weren't upset so much

00:10:04.640 --> 00:10:07.670
about Iran. The Lord said

00:10:07.680 --> 00:10:10.870
this was a red-headed stepchild to

00:10:10.880 --> 00:10:12.949
their faith.

00:10:12.959 --> 00:10:15.190
But Syria is pure blood to them; they're

00:10:15.200 --> 00:10:17.269
upset about this for some reason. And

00:10:17.279 --> 00:10:19.190
I don't understand all this

00:10:19.190 --> 00:10:19.200
stuff—the

00:10:19.200 --> 00:10:21.030
Shiites and the

00:10:21.040 --> 00:10:23.509
Sunnis and all that stuff. It's because,

00:10:23.519 --> 00:10:25.910
you know, it's just not what I know.

00:10:25.920 --> 00:10:27.509
But the Lord said, 'When they attack

00:10:27.519 --> 00:10:29.509
Syria, son, you're going to see a great

00:10:29.509 --> 00:10:29.519
uprising.'But

